<div align=\"center\">\n <br />\n <p>\: # Discord.js RPC Extension ### [Documentation](https://discord.js.org/#/docs/rpc/) ### [Rich Presence Example](https://github.com/discordjs/RPC/blob/master/example) ### __Browser__ Example ```javascript const clientId = '187406016902594560'; const scopes = ['rpc', 'rpc.api', 'messages.read']; const client = new RPC.Client({ transport: 'websocket' }); client.on('ready', () => { console.log('Logged in as', client.application.name); console.log('Authed for user', client.user.username); client.selectVoiceChannel('81384788862181376'); }); // Log in to RPC with client id client.login({ clientId, scopes }); ```
